ATTRIBUTION

axeVision is an independent reimplementation and full architectural rebuild, inspired by an original MVP concept called Weblenses, developed during the Feuji AI Innovate 2025 Hackathon by Team AIDucate. The original Weblenses project was a prototype consisting solely of a browser extension with snapshot functionality. axeVision shares no code with the original MVP and was designed, architected, and built entirely from scratch.

This attribution is included out of respect for the origin of the idea.

